pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Zambiri zomwe zili pa bolodi ili zimasonkhanitsidwa mwachindunji kuchokera ku mayankho a kafukufuku ndipo sizichokera ku ziwerengero zovomerezeka zamayiko kapena ma data. Ikuyimira malingaliro omwe achinyamata akuwonetsa panthawi ya kafukufukuyu, ndipo malingaliro aliwonse omwe amachokera ku mayankhowa ndi udindo wa wogwiritsa ntchito, osati PMNCH. PMNCH ikudzipereka kulemekeza, kulimbikitsa ndi kuteteza ufulu ndi ubwino wa anthu onse. Malingaliro aliwonse omwe aperekedwa muzoyankha pa kafukufukuyu kapena zolembedwa zotuluka m'dashboard iyi zomwe zikusemphana ndi kudziperekaku sizikuvomerezedwa ndi PMNCH.

wra03a-subtext: Pezani mayankho otseguka okwana 1.2 miliyoni kudzera pa bolodi lolumikizanali, chida chapadera chomwe chimalumikiza mawu a amayi ndi atsikana ndi kuthekera kosawerengeka kwa kusanthula kwa digito.
pmn01a-subtext: Takulandirani ku Dashboard ya “Zimene Achinyamata Amafuna”! Chida chothandizirachi chimapereka chithunzithunzi cha mayankho ndi zidziwitso zomwe tikusonkhanitsa kuchokera kwa achinyamata azaka zapakati pa 10-24 padziko lonse lapansi. Pachimake chazomwezo ndi funso lotseguka: "Kuti ndikhale ndi moyo wabwino, ndikufuna ...". Achinyamata ochokera padziko lonse lapansi akhala akuyankha izi, kutipatsa chidziwitso chapadera pa zosowa zawo, ziyembekezo, ndi zokhumba zawo. Onani zambiri, pezani nkhani za manambala, ndikugwirizana nafe kukulitsa mawu a achinyamata 1.8 biliyoni padziko lonse lapansi. Kuti mudziwe zambiri za kampeniyi, pitani ku http://www.1point8.org.
midwife-subtext: Tinafunsa azamba padziko lonse funso lakuti: “Kodi mumafuna chiyani kwambiri pa ntchito yanu monga mzamba?”
giz-subtext: Tinafunsa amayi 10603 ku Mexico funso lakuti, “Qué es lo que más deseas o necesitas para encontrar empleo o un mejor empleo? Por favor, comparte sólo la petición más importante para ti.“, (Kodi mukufuna chiyani kwambiri kapena mukufuna kuti mupeze ntchito kapena ntchito yabwino? Chonde gawanani zomwe zili zofunika kwambiri kwa inu.)
